WEBVTT

00:02.230 --> 00:03.630
Torchwood.

00:04.310 --> 00:07.090
Outside the
Government,beyond the police.

00:07.100 --> 00:10.180
Fighting for the future on
behalf of the human race.

00:11.280 --> 00:16.430
The 21st century is when everything
changes,and Torchwood is ready.

